description: Sprawling three bed, two bath duplex located in a boutique elevator building. Entryway opens up into a front-facing open concept living/dining area with hardwood floors and floor-to-ceiling windows. The modern kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, a breakfast bar, and ample storage space. The king sized master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and en-suite bath. Downstairs are two spacious bedrooms, a bathroom, and in-unit laundry. Additional features include central a/c, a bonus storage cage, and garage parking. Conveniently located within minutes of a wide variety of restaurants, bars, and shops on E and W Broadway. Available July 1. Parking available for an additional fee.
